reviewText: Compelling, moving, HOT! I bought this because I am a Jamie Dornan addict and he mentions in one of his many interviews that this is the first sexually explicit movies he saw. Actually, it's amazing that this came out in 1985, it feels very 2015. Don't miss this if you are a 50 Shades fan. You will see many similarities: the BDSM, the whips and belts, even  the sex with ice cubes scene, and -- spoiler alert here -- the ending.
The movie arrived promptly...a very enjoyable dvd!
